GIF Viewer playback fast-scaling pass
=====================================

Date: 2026-07-02

Project
-------
Source cloned from:
https://git.code.sf.net/p/gifviewer/git

Local source:
source

Purpose
-------
Improve GIF Viewer playback smoothness for large GIFs by avoiding expensive
GDI+ high-quality interpolation while animation is actively playing.

The app already has a Quality context-menu setting:
- Low    -> InterpolationMode.NearestNeighbor
- Medium -> InterpolationMode.High
- High   -> InterpolationMode.HighQualityBicubic

This change keeps the user's selected quality for paused/still display, but
temporarily uses the fast Low/nearest-neighbor path while playback is running.

