Notes
-----
This is intentionally a conservative first GIF Viewer change. It does not alter
decode, frame timing, frame disposal, memory settings, or the installed app. It
only makes active playback use the already-existing nearest-neighbor fast draw
path, then restores selected quality once playback stops.
